Scale interval definitions in theory/scale.rb are based on the Overtone project,
originally under the MIT license:
https://github.com/overtone/overtone/blob/master/LICENSE.

The copyright in Overtone is owned by the contributors named in its README file,
found at
https://github.com/overtone/overtone/blob/master/README.md.

---

