Many of the easing curve definitions in math/easings.rb are derived from the
easings.net project, particularly:
https://github.com/ai/easings.net/blob/master/src/easings.yml

The easings.net source code is under the GPLv3:
https://github.com/ai/easings.net/blob/master/LICENSE
